# Changelog

All notable changes to this project are documented in this file.

The format follows the principles of Keep a Changelog and Semantic Versioning.

---

## [1.0.0] - 2026-06

### Added

- Initial release of the Technical Documentation Generator extension.
- Support for generating README documentation.
- Support for generating User Guides.
- Support for generating API Documentation.
- Support for generating Technical Overviews.
- Support for generating Installation Guides.
- Support for generating Troubleshooting Guides.
- Support for generating Release Notes.
- Interactive documentation generation workflow.
- Markdown output support.
- Documentation preview.
- Searchable documentation templates.
- Command Palette integration.
- Reusable documentation templates.
- Input validation.
- Notification messages.
- Light and Dark theme support.

### Documentation

- Added README.
- Added User Guide.
- Added Installation Guide.
- Added Technical Overview.
- Added API Documentation.
- Added Troubleshooting Guide.
- Added Release Notes.
- Added Contributing Guide.
- Added License.

### Fixed

- Initial release.

### Known Limitations

- Markdown export only.
- Local file generation.
- No cloud synchronization.
- No AI-assisted documentation generation.
